      "bookSlug": "matthew",
      "chapterNumber": 14,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Matthew 14:18",
      "text": "ܐܡܪ ܠܗܘܢ ܝܫܘܥ ܐܝܬܘ ܐܢܘܢ ܠܝ ܠܗܪܟܐ ܀",
